      "description": "The following two requirements need configuration entries:\r\n * The location of the diagnostic script and its output folder (where the bundle will be saved) on the RM's filesystem should be configurable -\u00a0_script location; output folder_\r\n * The bundle can become large in size, so a configurable threshold functionality should be added. If the bundle's size exceeds the threshold the bundle will be stored in a local folder on the host of the RM, and the path will be returned\u00a0 -\u00a0_bundle forwarding size threshold_",
